{"id":621799,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/11/海外网-｜-暴徒泼油放火烧市民-香港光头警长怒斥/","date":"2019-11-11T10:14:56Z","modified":"2019-11-11T10:14:56Z","title":"海外网 ｜ 暴徒泼油放火烧市民 香港&#8221;光头警长&#8221;怒斥：人渣！","content":"<p>中国数字时代编辑注：目前该事件详细前因后果未知，仅转载中国官方媒体一种说法如下：</p>\n<p>海外网11月11日电 香港警队证实，11日中午，有香港暴徒在马鞍山向持不同意见的市民泼易燃液体放火。港媒称市民身体多处烧伤，已被送医治疗。香港“光头警长”在微博上怒斥暴徒“人渣！”</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_621803\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_2fb6d2ddcbae4e15b2867cfbf22c1f36.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-621803\" class=\"wp-image-621803\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_2fb6d2ddcbae4e15b2867cfbf22c1f36.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_2fb6d2ddcbae4e15b2867cfbf22c1f36.png 588w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_2fb6d2ddcbae4e15b2867cfbf22c1f36-273x300.png 273w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-621803\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">市民被暴徒泼易燃液体（东网）</p></div>\n<p>据“东网”等港媒报道，一名穿绿衣服的市民在一条连接马鞍山公园及海栢花园的行人天桥上，疑与人因政见问题发生肢体碰撞，其后被多人围堵理论。</p>\n<p>期间，一名身穿黑色衣裤戴口罩的男子突从人群冲出，向该市民淋泼易燃液体并点火，导致市民身体多处烧伤。现场人士见状纷纷走避，也有人试图追向纵火凶徒，沿途大叫“别走啊你”，伤者随后被送院治疗。</p>\n<p>港媒称，事发前有暴徒进入港铁马鞍山站大肆破坏，事主疑因不满车站被破坏而与在场黑衣人拉扯，其后追逐至上址，并与在场人士发生口角。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_621802\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_5106554a0e5748bf91c12c55d1cd82ed.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-621802\" class=\"wp-image-621802\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_5106554a0e5748bf91c12c55d1cd82ed.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_5106554a0e5748bf91c12c55d1cd82ed.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_5106554a0e5748bf91c12c55d1cd82ed-300x220.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-621802\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">市民多处被烧伤（东网）</p></div>\n<p>香港“东网”就事件向警方了解，初步确定事发今日(11日)下午近1时，警方将此案暂列袭击。</p>\n<p>事发后，被内地网友称为“光头警长”的香港警员刘sir在微博上连发两条微博，痛斥暴徒“人渣，竟然放火烧人，根本已经不可以叫他做人”“对着这班人渣，我们还可以说什么？！”</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_83b3b23b4f414191b68b74391afef69d.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-621801\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_83b3b23b4f414191b68b74391afef69d.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"171\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_83b3b23b4f414191b68b74391afef69d.jpeg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_83b3b23b4f414191b68b74391afef69d-300x103.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有外国网友将暴徒的恶行上传至推特等社交媒体，不少外国网友也震惊了，表示“天哪，这些自称示威者的人真是耻辱！”“这难道也叫‘民主自由’吗？这是恐怖主义！”</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_a65279274a3846569a942f7fa92916a5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-621800\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_a65279274a3846569a942f7fa92916a5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"458\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_a65279274a3846569a942f7fa92916a5.png 597w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2019_11_11_a65279274a3846569a942f7fa92916a5-300x275.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[38895,38912,38953,38919],"tags":[38564,39277,9503,39272,20761,38968,10155,23755]}